item.title: Can you turn a 317 into a 503?
item.dc:creator: @Yz85Racer Yz85Racer
item.description:
@Yz85Racer wrote:

503 is the version that saw the client’s graphics receive a hole make-over. It saw the full-screen addition, and a vast improvement.

Your server is built for the 317 protocol, so for it to become a 503 you’re going to have to change quite a bit. You’re better off writing your own base.
